cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting dl_carrierBandwidth to 300, which exceeds the maximum allowed PRBs for the frequency band, will cause configuration validation errors.
du.explanation_zh: 將 dl_carrierBandwidth 設定為 300，這超出頻率頻段允許的最大 PRB 數量，會導致配置驗證錯誤。
